## ⚠️ Challenges & Fixes

| Issue                   | Cause                    | Resolution                               |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------ | ---------------------------------------- |
| No data in Grafana      | Query not configured     | Added PromQL queries                     |
| Confusing UI            | Grafana UX complexity    | Used Prometheus query editor (Code mode) |
| Unit formatting missing | Incorrect unit selection | Set to `bytes (IEC)`                     |
| CRD sync failures       | ArgoCD patch limitation  | Enabled `Replace=true`                   |

